data.description: Move-in to this home by August, just in time for the new school year! Casual elegance defines the Bayberry single-family home: a plan both informal & inviting with unexpected architectural touches. The open flow makes this home ideal for entertaining friends & family. Unique spaces include the cozy & sophisticated study, oversized laundry room (convenient to the primary suite), and flexible loft space - ideal as a dedicated study space for the kids. Plus enjoy a finished basement with a private bedroom, a full bathroom, and a sizable walk-in closet. **Photos are of a similar completed home.
